  "special": {
    "title": "\"Did I fire six shots, or only five? Three? Seven. Whatever.\"",
    "description": "Consumes 3 ammo per shot (6 with Double Penetrating).\n\nFires one projectile that rapidly spawns six more, spreading horizontally. All projectiles deal explosive damage and explode on impact.\n\nCentre splash uses 100% grenade-damage scaling; spawned projectiles use 70%."
  },
  "notes": "Split distance scales with accuracy: higher accuracy delays the split.\n\nDouble Penetrating fires two parallel bursts, typically one beneath the other (can form an X), and uses 6 ammo per trigger pull.\n\nSpawned projectiles are not listed on the item card and each can receive full amp bonus.\n\nCentre projectile splash gets 100% grenade-damage scaling; side projectiles get 70%. Projectile speed boosts push the split farther out, hurting point-blank but improving longer-range consistency.",
